# Android Chrome — Editor Mobile Bugs (Custom Sections)

**Device**: One Plus 12, Android, Chrome browser  
**Feature**: "Add Section" / Custom Sections Before BOQ rich text editor  
**File**: `proposal-engine/frontend/src/components/CustomSectionsBeforeBoq.tsx`  
**Status**: All known issues addressed as of 2026-05-05. Needs real-device verification.

---

## What was reported

On Android Chrome (One Plus 12), the following toolbar actions **did not work**:
- Insert Table (nothing inserted)
- Italic toggle
- Font Color picker (color not applied)
- Highlight / Shading color picker (color not applied)
- Portrait orientation worse than landscape

---

